snippet.title: Battle Beans: Refried - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/864070/Battle_Beans_Refried

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/N8JKardv6j
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/battlebeansrefried
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Battle-Beans-Refried-107612252019034

Battle Beans: Refried is an Action-Packed, Round-Based, Third-Person Shooter where you must embody the power of the Bean! Shoot, Loot, and Destroy opponents in style with a vast collection of Weapons, Game Modes, Customization, Killstreaks, and more. Coming soon to Steam!
